## How It Works

This workflow uses a structured AI-guided process with {{STAGE_COUNT}} stages. At each stage, the AI:

- **Analyzes** your situation and asks clarifying questions when needed
- **Plans** the approach and gets your approval before executing
- **Produces** documented artifacts you can review
- **Tracks** all decisions so nothing is lost between sessions

